## Screen-by-Screen Specifications

---

### SCREEN 1 — Login (`/login`)

**Two-step layout — split screen**

**Left panel (dark, flex: 1)**
- `slate-900` background with subtle blue radial gradient
- SIMS DMS name, full institution name, tagline
- No interactive elements

**Right panel (white, 380px fixed)**

*Step 1 — Request OTP:*
- Title: "Sign in"
- Subtitle: "Enter your Telegram ID to receive your OTP"
- Input: "Telegram ID" — `@username or numeric ID`
- Info box (blue-50): explains OTP will arrive in Telegram Bot
- Button: "Send OTP" — full-width blue-600

*Step 2 — Enter OTP (replaces step 1 after send):*
- 6-digit OTP input — split into 6 individual boxes (monospace, 48px height)
- Countdown timer: "Expires in MM:SS" with Resend link
- Button: "Verify & Sign in" — full-width blue-600
- Error states: wrong OTP (red border on boxes), expired (amber message + new OTP prompt), locked (red alert, contact admin)

**Redirects after success:**
- `super_admin` → `/admin/dashboard` (full admin view)
- `admin` → `/admin/dashboard`
- `faculty` → `/faculty/dashboard`

---

### SCREEN 2 — Admin Dashboard (`/admin/dashboard`)

**Stat grid (4 columns):**
1. Faculty on duty today (blue accent) — count + breakdown (checked in / pending)
2. Violations this month (green accent) — count + weekly delta
3. Pending flags (amber accent) — count + CTA label
4. Open cover requests (red accent) — count

**Two-column grid below:**

*Left — Today's duty roster (table):*
- Columns: Faculty · Session · Status badge
- Shows only today's scheduled duty slots
- Status badges: Checked in (green), Late (amber), Pending (gray), Cover needed (orange)

*Right — Recent violations (table):*
- Columns: Student name + reg. number · Violation type · Fine
- "Flagged" amber badge where `is_flagged = true`
- Last 5 violations across all faculty

