### SCREEN 7 — Live Attendance (`/admin/attendance`)

**Auto-refreshes every 30 seconds via TanStack Query `refetchInterval: 30000`**

**Stat row (4 pills):**
- Checked in (green) · Late arrivals (amber) · Not checked in (red) · Auto clocked-out (blue)

**Faculty card grid (3 columns):**
Each card shows:
- Left border colour: green (IN) · amber (LATE) · gray (PENDING) · red (ABSENT)
- Faculty name + department
- Session badge (Morning / Afternoon)
- Status badge (IN / LATE / PENDING / ABSENT)
- Time: "In: HH:MM AM" or "Duty starts H:MM PM"

**Override action:** Admin can click a card → modal to set in_time / out_time manually with reason field

