## Component Specifications

### Button variants
| Variant | Style |
|---|---|
| `primary` | blue-600 bg, white text |
| `secondary` | slate-100 bg, slate-700 text, slate-200 border |
| `danger` | red-100 bg, red-600 text |
| `ghost` | transparent, slate-600 text, slate-100 on hover |

All sizes: default (7px 14px), `sm` (4px 10px)

### Modal
- Centered overlay (black 40% backdrop)
- White card, border-radius 12px, max-width 480px (sm) / 600px (lg)
- Header: title + ✕ close button
- Scrollable body
- Footer: Cancel + primary action buttons (right-aligned)

### Table
- `thead th`: 11px, 600 weight, uppercase, slate-500, letter-spacing .04em
- `tbody td`: 13px, slate-700, 10px 12px padding
- Row hover: slate-50 bg
- Divider: 1px slate-100 between rows

### Input / Select
- Border: slate-200, radius 8px, padding 9px 12px, 13px font
- Focus ring: blue-500 border + 3px rgba(59,130,246,.12) shadow
- Label: 12px, 600 weight, slate-600, 6px margin-bottom

### Pagination
- "Previous / Next" buttons
- Current page indicator
- Shown only when total > limit

### Toast
- Fixed bottom-right
- Green (success) / Red (error) / Amber (warning)
- Auto-dismiss after 3 seconds

