## PWA Requirements

- `manifest.json`: name "SIMS DMS", short_name "SIMS", theme_color #0f172a, background_color #f8fafc, display "standalone", icons at 192px and 512px
- `vite-plugin-pwa` with Workbox `generateSW` strategy
- Offline fallback page: "No internet connection — please reconnect to continue"
- Cache: API responses NOT cached (always fresh) — only static assets cached

---

## Responsive Behaviour

All screens are desktop-first with sidebar. On mobile (< 768px):
- Sidebar collapses to bottom tab bar (icons only, 5 primary tabs)
- Content area fills full width
- Table → card list view (each row becomes a stacked card)
- Modals → full-screen bottom sheet

---

## Accessibility

- All interactive elements have visible focus rings (blue-500 outline)
- Form labels always associated with inputs (htmlFor / id)
- Error messages associated with fields (aria-describedby)
- Loading states indicated by spinner or skeleton, not blank screens
- Buttons never disabled without a visible reason tooltip

